g.text: - Extended Client is an extension of standard AWS SQS client.
- Helps manage where messages are to large to send directly via Amazon SQS.
- Integrates Amazon S3 to store the message payload and sends a reference to SQS message.
- Useful when your message payload exceeds the 256kb size limit.
- You want to process large video, then the video will be uploaded to S3 and a reference to that video will
be stored in SQS. Video will be provided to consumer through S3 bucket automatically.
